author: noreply@blogger.com (Oggie Ramos)
title: Backpack Photography Invites You to Explore Maligcong
text: Saturday, August 1, 2015 Backpack Photography Invites You to Explore Maligcong Farther up from Bontoc is a quaint village of breathtaking terraces hemmed with stones, draped with clouds at sunrise and visited by fireflies at night. Come with us to Maligcong in time for the harvest season and come home with a yield of memorable images.
